Author: riplorena
Text: bro last time the munchies betrayed me , it was after a concert where I was incredibly high and had 4,000 calories lol, I feel this  Today the sugar cravings / munchies hit HARD and I had a pint of so delicious low calorie mousse ice cream w cherries. im probably gonna go over my cal limit but it was so good and not a full on binge! really filling sweet stuff like that helps (-:
